{
  "stem": "11771.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and after the [SIGHS] Russian occupation, we start to feel what that mean-- German occupation for Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One day, some difference-- I'd like to say-- orders for the Jewish people, like a Jew shouldn't go on the sidewalk-- should walk on the middle of the streets; announcing on the walls with big, official announcement, Jews should carry over to the authorities furs, silver, gold, livestocks, to the local authorities.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] They used to-- they form a judenrat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we used to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They used to-- the judenrat used to appoint work force for the German authority and for the Lithuanian authority, whenever there were request.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And [SIGHS] little by little, we adjust ourself under these new circumstances.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I used-- I was, at that time, about 15, 16 years old already-- 16 years old already.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I used to go to work, even I wasn't-- I don't need to go to work, 'cause of mine age.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I used to go to work instead of my father, because I didn't want to exploit my father to-- to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They used to-- like to say in English-- they used to laugh on-- from the Jewish who wears a beard.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Who wears payot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My father was a clean, with a little beard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They used to make jokes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they used to-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It wasn't-- so I was going for him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We was going to fixing the roads-- 10, 15, kilometers from every day, back and forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that wasn't the worst one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got to adjust ourself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They marched-- the worst thing the-- what they hurt my feeling, that we not allowed to walk on the sidewalks.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
